{"tid":12873,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"怕醫生割包皮出錯　腿上留言「不要割陰莖」","createTime":"2016-11-29T23:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T00:39:37.000Z","uid":12709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b802841d52eb42360828cefd428b80ba5913841","tid":12873,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/073542_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F073542_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8fd4ebe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/073547_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F073547_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=717f3544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國一名60歲男子佩頓(Sandy Paton)上周四割包皮，手術前他很擔心醫師會出錯，於是在大腿留言「不是割整條陰莖，只割包皮」。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，佩頓的手術順利完成，並已完全康復。他表示，唯一遺憾就是無法知道醫生看到留言後的反應，他說：「留言純屬搞笑，我很想看看醫生的表情，可惜醫生巡房時我的麻醉藥還沒退。」 佩頓的妻子安琪拉(Angela)形容丈夫手術後「走路好像約翰韋恩(John Wayne，60年代美國演員，常演牛仔英雄)一樣」。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"5470bf97e32098e5baff8b811cf88b24bdcdb6ad","tid":12873,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8db99b233d44b909403b5ba97aa5f62e745600e","tid":12873,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定係睇得我啲po多"},{"pid":"d63284f16764daab8d67dad0af55ae73d79b3b58","tid":12873,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T2